# Keep the Docker build context small and reproducible. Dependencies are installed inside the image
# (bun install), and build artifacts are regenerated, so none of these should be sent to the daemon.
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/.astro
**/dist
**/coverage

.git
.github
.vscode

**/*.log

# Never bake local secrets into an image.
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
